description = "Zhang Shun, the White Streak in the Waves. In the legend no man alive could match him underwater, where he drowned his enemies one by one. Here a canal fish-seller and peerless diver who can hold his breath longer than a man should live. Soft-spoken on land, lethal in any depth."
